sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant API as Presentation API
    participant BL as Business Logic
    participant DB as Persistence Database

    User->>API: Fill out place form
    Note over User, API: Requires user to be logged in
    API->>BL: Submit place data (API call)
    BL->>DB: Create place record
    DB-->>BL: Confirm record creation
    BL-->>API: Return new listing object
    API-->>User: Show success message
